              <span id="reviewTextContainer635309496" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10532817618090961884">Brilliant Book! Kept me engrossed the whole time reading it!<br/>The fact I grew up in Aughton/Ormskirk helped alot as I was able to picture a lot of the places mentioned and relate to a lot of the things going on.<br/>You really get the feeling you genuinely know the characters and you start feeling for them throughout their problems.<br/>Recommend this to anyone it has an appeal to both men and women, with love triangles, football, gangs, gambling etc. <br/><br/>Looking forward to the next book!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


