<span id="freeTextContainer12455169999543995549">I liked the way the book bounced between characters and time. I gave it a 4 star not because it was an great book but because I will miss the characters. it took me a few days to read the end because I was sad it was over and hate it when a book makes me cry =0) A unique story about a couples relationship from their courtship through his fight with cancer.</span>

